\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {B.1}{\ignorespaces  Moment--0 maps of the Per-emb-2 streamer with overlaid best-fit models obtained using different fitting strategies. The panels show the results from the grid search (\ref {fig:per2_mom0_grid_A}), the MCMC point-method posterior peak solution (\ref {fig:per2_mcmc_mom0_peak_grid_A}), and the MCMC point-method posterior median solution (\ref {fig:per2_mcmc_mom0_median_grid_A}). In each panel, the solid curve denotes the projected model streamer overlaid on the observed moment--0 emission, while the dots mark the positions extracted from the data and used for the point method. }}{53}{figure.caption.40}\protected@file@percent }
